        "text": "I am going into my third year of teaching at CWS, and I have been so impressed by the administration, facility, and community. This school aligns with my values- warmth and compassion for each child, an emphasis on the arts and movement, and learning that reflects the academic and developmental needs of the children. I also appreciate that the school supports teachers in continuing professional development each year. I would trust any of the teachers at this school to teach my child.",
