        "text": "Having 4 children and nannies and various private high end learning preschools.  Seedlings by far exceeds expectations.  My 4th child is attending the new and delightful centre in Scarboro.  The teachers are so caring and kind.  The creative play and singing and dancing are inspiring for the little ones.  The safety and details are always a consideration.  The outdoor play is excellent at this school.  I could not be happier with this wonderful environment for my last little one.  Excellent location, beautiful and a lovely Montessori school.",
