        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTimeDescription": "a year ago",
        "text": "Attention to detail is of the utmost importance at Cambridge Daycare. My son started there in 2014 and now my daughter is there and the staff is largely the same since we first arrived.\nThe friendliest atmosphere, the kids explore through arts and crafts and have the opportunity to read and be read to. It's an educational environment with a wide range of toys and puzzles that prepares kids for their schooling years. Staff take extra care to communicate how my child is behaving and cooperating with the others. Monthly emails reporting on activities and progress are sent and timely emails regarding changes in policies or important information keep parents up to date with expectations and requirements.\nI personally witnessed the work that went into the location change and the commitment made by everyone to make the transition. It is something to see. The layout of the new daycare is incomparable to any other. Plenty of open space with natural daylight streaming in, modernized kitchen, sinks and washrooms in every section. The pedway that centers the space is unique and beautifully constructed. The playground outside is inviting and spacious for kids to run and play.\nThere is a family feel to this place. I recommend it to anyone in search of a daycare for their child.",
